headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Get the White DJ Pooh Tee
content:
Pick up a coveted collector’s item and honor the legendary host of West Coast Classics by logging into GTA Online this week to receive the White WCC DJ Pooh Tee.

West Coast Classics is also the home of DJ Pooh's Dre Day Tribute — and completing The Data Leaks unlocks six Dr. Dre tracks in GTA Online that debuted in The Contract.
